      VALUES ('Amani Gardens Inn', 'amani-gardens-inn', '<p id="">Amani Gardens Inn has a 50-plus year reputation of warm hospitality and quiet gardens. Located in Westlands, we are centrally located in Nairobi and conveniently close to major shopping malls, banking centers, and restaurants, yet the place still retains the feel of a retreat in the countryside with our old English-style buildings and ancient trees. You can spend the morning quietly reading under a 75-year old jacaranda tree, or hop in a taxi and be exploring down town a few minutes later.&nbsp; </p><p id="">&nbsp;</p>', '<p><span><span><span>Spacious gardens, friendly staff, rooms with locally inspired decor and traditional American food bring our guests back again and again.&nbsp; We offer a variety of rooms to accommodate your budget. We have rooms with a private balcony or porch and rooms with ensuite bathrooms and private rooms with shared bathroom and shower facilities. </span></span></span></p><p><span><span><span>Amani Gardens Inn was formerly known as the Mennonite Guest House and we are still owned by Eastern Mennonite Missions.&nbsp; Amani means peace in Kiswahili.&nbsp; Peace is an important distinctive of Mennonites.&nbsp; We hope you find peace while staying at Amani Gardens Inn.</span></span></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'https://media-dev.exploro.com/inflight-media/Banner%2B1440x630%2BAmaniGarden.jpg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cb055decda57c60cbcb450_Banner%252B1440x630%252BAmaniGarden.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d940f3238be3_63cc52e0440ed70117e55523_carousel4.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95fa9238be0_63cc52e0d805d5e780eb6429_carousel5_0.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d94a35238be1_63cc52e00760e7cc4234f478_carousel1.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95c84238be4_63cc52e0d7632e162