      VALUES ('Comfy Inn Eldoret', 'comfy-inn-eldoret', '<p id="">Comfy Inn’s new and expanded Eldoret location represents a truly <strong id="">authentic</strong> hotel, featuring excellent accommodations and conference facilities as well as breakfasts of fresh croissants and steaming bowls of café.&nbsp; Comfy Inn Hotel is located in the Central Business District (CBD) of Eldoret town, one of the fastest growing agricultural regions in north rift Kenya. The hotel is only 12 kilometers from the Eldoret International Airport and is in close proximity to the central business district to ensure guests enjoy the convenience of shopping malls, social amenities and offices. We have ample, secure parking and complimentary and fast WIFI.</p><p id="">&nbsp;</p>', '<p><span><span><span>Comfy Inn Hotel&nbsp; features 96 spacious guest rooms and bathrooms that combine comfort, style, elegance and the latest technology making it an ideal place for leisure &amp; travel.&nbsp; The soothing palette of warm colors along with the branded furniture, combine the classical with the modern to create a beautiful and cosy atmosphere.</span></span></span></p><p><span><span><span><span lang="DA">The Comfy </span><span>Inn </span><span lang="DA">Conference Cent</span><span>re</span><span lang="DA"> is now the epitome of conferences, relaxation, learning, invigoration, purification, rejuvenation and general well-being. The centre has a lounge</span><span> and </span><span lang="DA">two boardrooms with state of the art conferencing facilities.</span></span></span></span></p><p><span><span><span><span lang="DA">Our outstanding restaurant awaits to tempt our guests with international culinary delights. Sumptuous buffets are available in the </span><span>r</span><span lang="DA">estaurant for breakfast and dinner. We offer local cuisine for lunch and dinner and promise fine dining with our chefs creating gourmet dishes in an open kitchen environment.</span></span></span></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 