      VALUES ('Cozy Point Home', 'cozy-point-home', '<p id="">The five rooms concept hotel blends the essence of the owner''s love for inviting people to explore, enjoy, eat, drink, sing, dance, swim, sun, and simply BE TOGETHER.</p><p id="">&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Stepping in Cozy Point and breathing Africa in its essence is a moment of magic. The concept hotel blends the traditions of Malindi and takes inspiration from there for the choice of colors, materials, furnishings, and decorations, creating an authentic and welcoming environment. The owners will be on-site to help you day after day to live your requests and surprise you with ideas and proposals resulting from 20 years of experience in Kenya. Their hospitality, sense of taste, and attention to detail is a true experience in itself, and your holiday will bring many memories to your heart.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'https://media-dev.exploro.com/inflight-media/1920%2520x%25201080%2520Cozy%2520Point%2520Home%2520Malindi.jpg', '', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d940f3238be3_63cc52e0440ed70117e55523_carousel4.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95fa9238be0_63cc52e0d805d5e780eb6429_carousel5_0.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d94a35238be1_63cc52e00760e7cc4234f478_carousel1.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95c84238be4_63cc52e0d7632e1626418c7f_carousel3.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d970ed238be2_63cc52e00760e7280834f479_carousel2.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cb055c21fb70a062721702_cozy-overview.jpeg', ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5ac08de9f2d81a3c8e96_63cb7b08d7632edf2133f782_6.png; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5ac08de9f2b7723c8e95_63cb7b055c439a4aac82bb90_7.png; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed4796