      VALUES ('Crowne Plaza Hamburg', 'crowne-plaza-hamburg', '<p id="">The 4-star Crowne Plaza® Hamburg - City Alster is located near the center of Hamburg, in the popular St. Georg / Hohenfelde area near Alster Lake. The main train station, the city center, Jungfernstieg and the Europapassage as well as the main sights of Hamburg are all located in the immediate vicinity of the hotel. The Crowne Plaza® Hamburg - City Alster was recently renovated in 2019 to meet the needs of the modern business traveler. &nbsp;The rooms are spacious and multi-functional and there are multiple restaurants with popular classics and specialty cuisines.</p>', '<p>Crowne Plaza Hamburg offers 291 soundproof guest rooms, a restaurant, a fitness center, and a bar/lounge. There is a highly functioning Business Center and nine conference rooms, complimentary WiFi, and internet access in public areas. The Plaza Workspace is the perfect place to meet friends or colleagues or work in a relaxed manner. The rooms offer calming accents and multi-functional space to ensure relaxation and productivity. In addition to renovated rooms, there is an innovative all-day culinary concept and new inspiring meeting rooms and co-working spaces. This upmarket hotel is in a great location near the Uhlandstrasse U-Bahn Station and Planten un Blomen Park.</p>', 'https://media-dev.exploro.com/inflight-media/CROWNE+PLAZA+.mp4', '', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d940f3238be3_63cc52e0440ed70117e55523_carousel4.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95fa9238be0_63cc52e0d805d5e780eb6429_carousel5_0.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d94a35238be1_63cc52e00760e7cc4234f478_carousel1.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95c84238be4_63cc52e0d7632e1626418c7f_carousel3.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d970ed238be2_63cc52e00760e728