      VALUES ('Fairmont Hotel Vier Jahreszeiten', 'fairmont-hotel-vier-jahreszeiten', '<p id="">Luxurious Fairmont Hotel Vier Jahreszeiten is the epitome of a traditional European grand hotel. Since its opening in 1897, the elegant hotel at the Inner Alster Lake in the heart of Hamburg, welcomes its guests from all over the world in charming magnificence and timeless elegance. Many cultural and architectural sights as well as numerous shopping areas and the Congress Center Hamburg are within close distance.</p>', '<p>Fairmont Hotel Vier Jahreszeiten is your home away from home, located in the heart of Hamburg, where you can benefit from the charm of a grand hotel with more than 120 years of heritage. We not only fulfill international standards, but we set them. Our beautiful accommodations include guest rooms and suites with breathtaking views, timeless charm, and elegance. Our 24-hour Concierge and reception desk will be delighted to assist you in making your stay as comfortable as possible. Enjoy our multiple restaurants and bars, which offer a wide variety of cuisine and drinks. The Vier Jahreszeiten Spa &amp; Fitness Center offers its guests a unique oasis of well-being where you can discover pure relaxation. Soak up a mix of medieval flair and cosmopolitan lifestyle reminiscent of the Hamptons.</p>', 'https://media-dev.exploro.com/inflight-media/FAIRMONT+HOTEL+VIER+JAHRESZEITEN+.mp4', '', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d940f3238be3_63cc52e0440ed70117e55523_carousel4.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95fa9238be0_63cc52e0d805d5e780eb6429_carousel5_0.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d94a35238be1_63cc52e00760e7cc4234f478_carousel1.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95c84238be4_63cc52e0d7632e1626418c7f_carousel3.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d970ed238be2_63cc52