      VALUES ('Hotels in Kuala Lumpur', 'hotels-in-kuala-lumpur', '', '<p>Set amidst the heart of Kuala Lumpur''s Golden Triangle, Banyan Tree Kuala Lumpur offers 55 rooms and suites with a contemporary flair. Most of the guestrooms overlook the iconic Petronas Twin Towers and Kuala Lumpur Tower and each designed to bring comfort to those seeking a true Sanctuary for the Senses. Be awed by the panoramic view of the city skyline from Vertigo, the rooftop bar and Horizon Grill, the exquisite steakhouse, or be pampered at the award-winning Banyan Tree Spa.</p><p>Populated by Malays, Chinese, Indians and indigenous groups, Malaysia boasts a rich cultural heritage. Whether it is the old world charm or the modern sophistication, there will always be some fascinating sights to experience.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'https://media-dev.exploro.com/inflight-media/kl-hotels-banner.jpg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cb0557d7632e2e322a53ae_kl-hotels-banner.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d940f3238be3_63cc52e0440ed70117e55523_carousel4.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95fa9238be0_63cc52e0d805d5e780eb6429_carousel5_0.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d94a35238be1_63cc52e00760e7cc4234f478_carousel1.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95c84238be4_63cc52e0d7632e1626418c7f_carousel3.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d970ed238be2_63cc52e00760e7280834f479_carousel2.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cb0557d7632e24d52a53c3_bayantree-overview.jpeg', ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5ac08de9f2d81a3c8e96_63cb7b08d7632edf2133f782_6.png; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5ac08de9f2b7723c8e95_63cb7b055c439a4aac82bb90_7.png; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fe