      VALUES ('Hotels in Nairobi', 'hotels-in-nairobi', '', '<p>Hotel Tobriana has been built lovingly with the best workmanship and rustic Kenyan materials that literally takes hospitality to new heights.<br /><br />Right as you enter the hotel gates, you''ll get that sense of warmth and a sense of familiarity that will make you feel comfortable and unearth that spirit of unceasing adventure.<br /><br />We''ve pushed the limits on every avenue to ensure we have amenities to support fun activities at multiple levels so that you and your family can enjoy a wholesome weekend or vacation at the hotel. Nothing beats enjoying life in an environment that is entertaining and as empowering... so spoil yourself, come enjoy unspoilt nature at Hotel Tobriana.<br /><br />We believe that key to our success, is characterised by our people. Therefore, we are committed to achieving success by combining the traditions of our local community to the exceptional services provided in our hotel.<br /><br />Stay for a night, leave with a story!</p>', 'https://media-dev.exploro.com/inflight-media/1440_630_Hotels_1.png', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cb055f993f0012cd2e1bd0_1440_630_Hotels_1.png', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d940f3238be3_63cc52e0440ed70117e55523_carousel4.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95fa9238be0_63cc52e0d805d5e780eb6429_carousel5_0.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d94a35238be1_63cc52e00760e7cc4234f478_carousel1.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95c84238be4_63cc52e0d7632e1626418c7f_carousel3.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d970ed238be2_63cc52e00760e7280834f479_carousel2.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cb055f0949d901e40d9529_tobriana-overview.jpeg', ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e