      VALUES ('Hyperion Hotel', 'hyperion-hotel', '<p id="">Hyperion Hotel is a 5-star luxury hotel in Hamburg-Mitt, that is connected to the convention center. The rooms in the Hyperion Hotel Hamburg offer the highest level of comfort for a pleasant stay. Each of the spacious rooms has individually adjustable air conditioning, a seating area as well as a coffee and tea station, and a minibar. A modern flat screen TV including Sky Sport is also available to you. The elegant bathroom facilities promise moments of relaxation with a large rainforest shower, hairdryer, cosmetic mirror, towel warmer, and high-quality care products.</p>', '<p>The Hyperion Hotel Hamburg, which opened in October 2015, welcomes you near Hamburg''s HafenCity. Individually adjustable air conditioning, WiFi, and TV promise comfort in the 254 modern guest rooms and suites. There is an underground car park with 106 parking spaces to serve our guests. The hotel offers an extensive breakfast buffet in the morning and à la carte indulgence in the "Gaumenfreund" restaurant for lunch and dinner. The hotel bar, Hamburg 11, on the eleventh floor, is just the right place to relax at the end of the day with a drink. There are a wellness and fitness area with a fitness room, a whirlpool tub and sauna, and eleven fully equipped meeting rooms. The events team will be happy to help with planning and implementation of meetings and events. Whether on a fun city trip or as part of a business appointment, experience the comfort of the Hyperion Hotel Hamburg while visiting the great city of Hamburg.&nbsp;</p>', 'https://media-dev.exploro.com/inflight-media/HYPERION+HOTEL.mp4', '', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d940f3238be3_63cc52e0440ed70117e55523_carousel4.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95fa9238be0_63cc52e0d805d5e780eb6429_carousel5_0.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d94a35238be1_63cc52e0