      VALUES ('ibis Styles Bangkok Khaosan Viengtai', 'ibis-styles-bangkok-khaosan-viengtai', '<p id="">Strategically located in the heart of the Khaosan Road area, the traveler hub of Bangkok, ibis Styles Bangkok Khaosan Viengtai is a stylish 3-star hotel that offers guests a stay in Bangkok''s historic old quarter. Revered for its stunning architecture and rich culture, you''ll find the old quarter bursting at the seams with street food, cultural attractions, and local entertainment on every corner.</p><p id="">&nbsp;</p>', '<p>The safety and hygiene of our valued guests is our number one priority. As a result of our stringent quality, social distancing and hygiene preparations, ibis Styles Bangkok Khaosan Viengtai is pleased to announce our Safety &amp; Health Administration (SHA) certification, issued by the Tourism Authority of Thailand (TAT). Another vital certification the hotel is proud to receive is the ALLSAFE Cleanliness &amp; Prevention Label. This has been developed in cooperation by Accor and Bureau Veritas, one of the world leaders in inspection and certification. All Accor Group hotels that receive this accreditation will also be audited by Accor’s own auditors and third-party auditors as well.</p><p>Choose your room from one of our 4 categories including standard, twin bed setup, triple bunk bed rooms, family rooms. All rooms come with free breakfast and wifi, so you can enjoy your stay within the comfort of ibis Styles Bangkok Khaosan Viengtai.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'https://media-dev.exploro.com/inflight-media/banner_13.jpg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cb0554763a9e5df9306bed_banner_13.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d940f3238be3_63cc52e0440ed70117e55523_carousel4.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95fa9238be0_63cc52e0d805d5e780eb6429_carousel5_0.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d94a35238be1_6