      VALUES ('ibis Styles Kota Bharu Hotel', 'ibis-styles-kota-bharu-hotel', '<p id="">ibis Styles Kota Bharu is situated at Kota Bharu town centre by the Kelantan river. It is nestled next to the new Kelantan state palace. KB Mall only 3 minutes away and AEON Mall, the largest shopping mall in Kota Bharu is only 7 minutes drive from the hotel. To the famous Siti Khadijah market is only 7 minutes drive from the hotel. To famous Night Market at Wakaf Che Yeh only 10 minutes drive and Golf Course only 22 minutes away.</p>', '<p>Set in Kota Bharu, Kelantan region, ibis Styles Kota Bharu is located 1.4 km from Bus &amp; Teksi Station. Featuring a 24-hour front desk, this property also has a restaurant and an outdoor pool. The accommodation offers room service, a kids'' club and currency exchange for guests.</p><p>Guests at the hotel can enjoy a continental breakfast.</p><p>Ibis Styles Kota Bharu offers a children''s playground. Guests at the accommodation will be able to enjoy activities in and around Kota Bharu, like fishing.</p><p>Guests can make use of the business centre, work out at the gym or relax in the snack bar.</p><p>Popular points of interest near ibis Styles Kota Bharu include Kota Bharu Mall, Handicraft Village and Craft Museum and Billion Shopping Centre. The nearest airport is Sultan Ismail Petra Airport, 8 km from the hotel.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'https://media-dev.exploro.com/inflight-media/banner_11.jpg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cb05560760e749401fce14_banner_11.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d940f3238be3_63cc52e0440ed70117e55523_carousel4.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95fa9238be0_63cc52e0d805d5e780eb6429_carousel5_0.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d94a35238be1_63cc52e00760e7cc4234f478_carousel1.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95c84238be4_63cc