      VALUES ('ibis Styles Kota Kinabalu Inanam Hotel', 'ibis-styles-kota-kinabalu-inanam-hotel', '<p id="">Located in the bustling commercial township of Inanam, ibis Styles Kota Kinabalu Inanam features 184 rooms with free high speed WiFi, restaurant, bar, gym, event halls and a Sky Dex on the top floor overlooking the lush green landscape.</p><p id="">Kota Kinabalu is the capital of the Sabah, Malaysia. A coastal city partly surrounded by rainforest, it is known for its bustling markets, modern boardwalk and beaches.</p><p id="">&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Nestled in the heart of Central Business District,&nbsp;<strong>ibis Styles Kota Kinabalu Inanam</strong>&nbsp;is an ideal spot from which to discover Kota Kinabalu. From here, guests can make the most of all that the lively city has to offer. With its convenient location, the property offers easy access to the city''s must-see destinations.<br /><br />All the services and amenities you have come to expect from Accor Hotels are&nbsp;right in the comfort of your own home. This property offers numerous on-site facilities to satisfy even the most discerning guest.<br /><br />All guest accommodations feature thoughtful amenities to ensure an unparalleled sense of comfort. The property''s host of recreational offerings ensures you have plenty to do during your stay.&nbsp;<strong>ibis Styles Kota Kinabalu Inanam</strong>&nbsp;is an ideal place of stay for travelers seeking charm, comfort, and convenience in Kota Kinabalu.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'https://media-dev.exploro.com/inflight-media/ibis-kota-banner.jpg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cb05560760e712ca1fce15_ibis-kota-banner.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d940f3238be3_63cc52e0440ed70117e55523_carousel4.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95fa9238be0_63cc52e0d805d5e780eb6429_carousel5_0.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d9