      VALUES ('Mercure Penang Beach', 1, '<p id="">Located in Kota Kinabalu, the capital city of Sabah, Mercure Kota Kinabalu City Centre is within walking distance from banks, shopping malls, restaurants, tourist attractions and the historical Jesselton Point Waterfront. It also has easy access to the new convention centre - Sabah International Convention Centre (SICC). In addition, the hotel is only 15 minutes by car from Kota Kinabalu International Airport.</p><p id="">&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Whether you''re a tourist or traveling on business,&nbsp;<strong>Mercure Kota Kinabalu City Centre</strong>&nbsp;is a great choice for accommodation when visiting Kota Kinabalu. From here, guests can enjoy easy access to all that the lively city has to offer. With its convenient location, the hotel offers easy access to the city''s must-see destinations.<br /><br />The facilities and services provided by&nbsp;<strong>Mercure Kota Kinabalu City Centre</strong>&nbsp;ensure a pleasant stay for guests. This hotel offers numerous on-site facilities to satisfy even the most discerning guest.<br /><br />In addition, all guestrooms feature a variety of comforts. Many rooms even provide internet access – wireless, air conditioning, satellite/cable TV, shower, hair dryer to please the most discerning guest. Besides, the hotel''s host of recreational offerings ensures you have plenty to do during your stay. Whatever your reason for visiting Kota Kinabalu, the&nbsp;<strong>Mercure Kota Kinabalu City Centre</strong>&nbsp;is the perfect venue for an exhilarating and exciting break away.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'https://media-dev.exploro.com/inflight-media/penang-banner.jpg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cb055ad802df2ec065710a_penang-banner.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d940f3238be3_63cc52e0440ed70117e55523_carousel4.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95fa9238be0_63cc52e0d805d5e780eb6