      VALUES ('Ngulia Safari Lodge', 'ngulia-safari-lodge', '<p id="">Ngulia Safari Lodge is located in Tsavo and is a 3-star lodge with full-service spa, business center, an outdoor pool, and a restaurant all available for your use in a smoke-free environment. &nbsp;Local points of interest include Tsavo West National Park and Chaimu Crater Viewpoint.</p><p id="">&nbsp;</p>', '<p>3-star lodge with full-service spa, business center, an outdoor pool, and a restaurant all available for your use at this smoke-free lodge. WiFi in public areas is free. Other amenities include a bar/lounge, a poolside bar, and spa services. All 52 rooms offer room service, premium bedding, and free bottled water. Other amenities available to guests include ceiling fans, showers, and desks.</p><p>Ngulia Safari Lodge offers 52 accommodations with complimentary bottled water and ceiling fans. Beds feature premium bedding. Bathrooms include showers and complimentary toiletries. Irons/ironing boards and hair dryers can be requested. Cribs/infant beds (complimentary) are also available. Housekeeping is provided daily.</p><p>Recreational amenities at the lodge include an outdoor pool along with many optional activities available on site or nearby, fees may apply.</p><p>Guests can indulge in a pampering treatment at the lodge''s full-service spa. Services include facials, body treatments, and manicures and pedicures.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'https://media-dev.exploro.com/inflight-media/Ngulia-Banner.jpg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cb0560835384eb244b5ee6_Ngulia-Banner.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d940f3238be3_63cc52e0440ed70117e55523_carousel4.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95fa9238be0_63cc52e0d805d5e780eb6429_carousel5_0.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d94a35238be1_63cc52e00760e7cc4234f478_carousel1.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.c