      VALUES ('Novotel Bangkok Ploenchit Sukhumvit', 'novotel-bangkok-ploenchit-sukhumvit', '<p id="">Novotel Bangkok Ploenchit Sukhumvit is located in the city centre, near Ploenchit BTS Skytrain Station. A convenient location for both business and leisure stays. Guests are within easy walking distance to Central Embassy and Sukhumvit Road. Nearby attractions and shopping malls include Siam Paragon, Siam Square and The Emquatier. Relax in 4-star comfort, with our 370 guest rooms, free WIFI and 12 meeting rooms. Unwind with our outdoor swimming pool and gym with sauna, or get a drink at Beer Garden.</p>', 'Located next to Ploenchit sky train station, offering easy access to Bangkok CBD including Silom, Sathorn and Sukhumvit. Shopping malls, restaurants and spas are within walking distance or easily accessed via sky train. Local restaurants, bars and spas are within walking distance or easily accessed via sky train. Nearby attractions include Jim Thompson House, Sea Life Bangkok, Erawan Shrine (Four Faced Buddha) as well as the riverside and temples tour. From breakfast to lunch, dinner or a tasty little snack, Novotel provides balanced choices and à la carte service 24/7 at all its hotels. At Novotel, you can count on enjoying a relaxing meal in a friendly, stylish setting.', 'https://media-dev.exploro.com/inflight-media/banner1.jpg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cb0555ea97bee1bab34a7c_banner1.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d940f3238be3_63cc52e0440ed70117e55523_carousel4.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95fa9238be0_63cc52e0d805d5e780eb6429_carousel5_0.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d94a35238be1_63cc52e00760e7cc4234f478_carousel1.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95c84238be4_63cc52e0d7632e1626418c7f_carousel3.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed