      VALUES ('Novotel Kuala Lumpur City Centre', 1, '<p id="">Novotel stands in the Golden Triangle of Kuala Lumpur between Petronas Twin Towers and Bukit Bintang shopping district. Guests can enjoy meals at the in-house restaurant or have a drink at the bar. Free WiFi is available throughout the property.</p><p id="">It is 121 m to Pavilion Shopping Mall and 300 m to Aquaria KLCC, while Petronas Twin Towers and Suria KLCC are 851 m away. Rajah Chulan LRT Station is 400 m from Novotel Kuala Lumpur City Center. Kuala Lumpur International Airport is 40 mi from the property.</p><p id="">&nbsp;</p>', 'Novotel Kuala Lumpur City Centre is located in the Golden Triangle of Kuala Lumpur between PETRONAS Twin Towers and Bukit Bintang, less than 5 mins walk to Kuala Lumpur Convention Centre. Major shopping malls Suria KLCC and Pavilion KL are accessible using the skybridge. Lift modernization works are being carried out now till Sept 2021. There will be still lift running to the floors. Premier Lounge is closed. Renovation works from Mondays - Fridays 9:00AM - 6:00PM, Saturdays 10:00AM - 5:00PM.</p><p>All 302 rooms offer free WiFi, TVs with satellite channels, 24-hour room service, free bottled water, coffee/tea corner, hairdryer, and in-room safe, designed with everything you need for a relaxing stay. Novotel Kuala Lumpur is located in the city centre, less than 5 mins walk to Kuala Lumpur Convention Centre (KLCC) and Pavilion shopping centre, close to train station and entertainment hub, perfect for leisure or business.', 'https://media-dev.exploro.com/inflight-media/novotel-banner.jpg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cb055727e7bcb71be72ee7_novotel-banner.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d940f3238be3_63cc52e0440ed70117e55523_carousel4.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95fa9238be0_63cc52e0d805d5e780eb6429_carousel5_0.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be35