      VALUES ('Pavilion Hotel Kuala Lumpur Managed By Banyan Tree', 'pavilion-hotel-kuala-lumpur-managed-by-banyan-tree', '<p id="">Pavilion Hotel Kuala Lumpur Managed by Banyan Tree features 325 spaciously appointed rooms and suites, and three specialty outlets. An elegant pillar-less ballroom and six multi-event spaces all with natural daylight are available. With direct connection to Pavilion Kuala Lumpur, guests are able to enjoy premier luxury retail temptations and entertainment.</p><p id="">&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Located in the heart of Bukit Bintang, Pavilion Hotel Kuala Lumpur offers 325 beautifully appointed rooms and suites with club floor facilities to discerning business and leisure travellers who want a more personalised service. For dining experiences, the re are an all-day dining restaurant named The Courtyard offering authentic Southeast Asian cuisine; Ebisu, a Japanese fusion restaurant; and Whisky Cove, a whisky bar. The Banyan Tree Spa and seven multi-event spaces are also available in the hotel.</p><p>Populated by Malays, Chinese, Indians and indigenous groups, Malaysia boasts a rich cultural heritage. Whether it is the old world charm or the modern sophistication, there will always be some fascinating sights to experience.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'https://media-dev.exploro.com/inflight-media/pavilion-managed-banner.jpg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cb0559b627335f500622b6_pavilion-managed-banner.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d940f3238be3_63cc52e0440ed70117e55523_carousel4.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95fa9238be0_63cc52e0d805d5e780eb6429_carousel5_0.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d94a35238be1_63cc52e00760e7cc4234f478_carousel1.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95c84238be4_63cc52e0d7632e1626418c7f_carousel3.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be3