      VALUES ('Pullman Miri Waterfront Hotel 5 stars', 'pullman-miri-waterfront-hotel-5-stars', '<p id="">Miri is a coastal city in Sarawak, Malaysia, located near the border of Brunei. It serves as a passageway to Gunung Mulu National Park, a UNESCO World Heritage Site.</p><p id="">328 full service hotel rooms, restaurants and bars, ballrooms and meeting rooms, with a gym and Spa. The hotel is elegant in style, offering the ultimate luxury experience. The scenic views fronting the South China Sea, Miri River and the city makes it an ideal option for both a relaxing getaway, dining and business meetings in breathtaking.</p>', '<p>Pullman Miri Waterfront is a 5-star hotel in Miri, home to 19 of Sarawak''s 32 ethnic groups and some of the world''s most spectacular natural wonders. The 328-room full-service hotel is casually elegant in style, smart architectural and relaxed in spirit for ultimate luxury experience. Fronting the South China Sea, Miri River estuary and the city for both relaxing getaways and business.</p>', 'https://media-dev.exploro.com/inflight-media/banner_5.jpg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cb05585c56b2d8d9475b26_banner_5.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d940f3238be3_63cc52e0440ed70117e55523_carousel4.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95fa9238be0_63cc52e0d805d5e780eb6429_carousel5_0.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d94a35238be1_63cc52e00760e7cc4234f478_carousel1.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95c84238be4_63cc52e0d7632e1626418c7f_carousel3.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d970ed238be2_63cc52e00760e7280834f479_carousel2.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cb05585c56b2521e475b25_hotel.jpeg', ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5ac08de9f2d81a3c8e96_6