      VALUES ('Restaurants in Kota Bharu', 1, '', '<p>Set in Kota Bharu, Kelantan region, ibis Styles Kota Bharu is located 1.4 km from Bus &amp; Teksi Station. Featuring a 24-hour front desk, this property also has a restaurant and an outdoor pool. The accommodation offers room service, a kids'' club and currency exchange for guests.</p><p>Guests at the hotel can enjoy a continental breakfast.</p><p>Ibis Styles Kota Bharu offers a children''s playground. Guests at the accommodation will be able to enjoy activities in and around Kota Bharu, like fishing.</p><p>Guests can make use of the business centre, work out at the gym or relax in the snack bar.</p><p>Popular points of interest near ibis Styles Kota Bharu include Kota Bharu Mall, Handicraft Village and Craft Museum and Billion Shopping Centre. The nearest airport is Sultan Ismail Petra Airport, 8 km from the hotel.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'https://media-dev.exploro.com/inflight-media/kotabharu-restobanner.jpg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cb0556c5f7cd0cfb7fe616_kotabharu-restobanner.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d940f3238be3_63cc52e0440ed70117e55523_carousel4.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95fa9238be0_63cc52e0d805d5e780eb6429_carousel5_0.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d94a35238be1_63cc52e00760e7cc4234f478_carousel1.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95c84238be4_63cc52e0d7632e1626418c7f_carousel3.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d970ed238be2_63cc52e00760e7280834f479_carousel2.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d06ffa8217f1e83ab82a_overview_2.jpeg', ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5ac08de9f2d81a3c8e96_63cb7b08d7632edf2133f782_6.png; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5ac08de9f2b