      VALUES ('The Lawford Hotel', 'the-lawford-hotel', '<p id="">With its lush vegetation, dreamy landscape and warm-hearted people, the Lawford Hotel is a true oasis for the body and soul. It is located in the center of Malindi, on the shores of the ocean, among dunes, palms and frangipanis.&nbsp; Our mission is for our guests to have a relaxing time and enjoy total privacy during their stay in one of our beautiful villas or suites. At The Lawford Hotel, time stands still, and moments are colored by irresistible sunsets.</p><p id="">&nbsp;</p>', '<p><span><span><span>The Lawford Hotel, located in Malindi Town, is within walking distance from shops, boutiques, restaurants and the Casino is nestled in a magnificent tropical garden teeming with native plants, and overlooking a wide beach.&nbsp; Its grounds cover over 6 hectares (14.8 acres) and its extensive and immaculate garden hosts 2 swimming pools and landscaped areas for relaxation.&nbsp; Our staff are professional, attentive and friendly and every effort is made to make your stay comfortable and enjoyable.</span></span></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'https://media-dev.exploro.com/inflight-media/Dave+and+Tracey-+Highlight+Clip+-+30sec-+83mb.mp4', '', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d940f3238be3_63cc52e0440ed70117e55523_carousel4.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95fa9238be0_63cc52e0d805d5e780eb6429_carousel5_0.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d94a35238be1_63cc52e00760e7cc4234f478_carousel1.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95c84238be4_63cc52e0d7632e1626418c7f_carousel3.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d970ed238be2_63cc52e00760e7280834f479_carousel2.jpeg', '', ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5ac08de9f2d81a3c8e96_63cb7b08d7632edf2133f782_6.png; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63b