      VALUES ('The Park Lane Hong Kong', 'the-park-lane-hong-kong', '<p id="">Angsana Teluk Bahang, Penang, is the first Angsana brand in Malaysia, managed by Banyan Tree Hotels and Resorts. The 250 keys vibrant resort sits on idyllic Teluk Bahang beach, offers contemporary rooms and suites with modern amenities. Popular tourist attractions are located nearby the resort. Facilities and services include five food and beverage outlets, a ballroom, three meeting rooms, two swimming pools, one children''s pool, a kids club, wellness center, fitness center, spa and gallery.</p><p id="">&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Set in Teluk Bahang, 1.7 mi from Batu Ferringhi Beach, Angsana Teluk Bahang offers accommodations with a restaurant, free private parking, an outdoor swimming pool and a fitness center. Each accommodations at the 5-star hotel has sea views, and guests can enjoy access to a bar and to a terrace. The accommodations features a 24-hour front desk, a shuttle service, room service and free WiFi throughout the property.</p><p>All guest rooms at the hotel come with air conditioning, a seating area, a flat-screen TV with satellite channels, a safety deposit box and a private bathroom with a bidet, bathrobes and slippers. The rooms will provide guests with a desk and a kettle.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'https://media-dev.exploro.com/inflight-media/angsanabahang-banner.jpg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cb05568de9f23e6e272893_angsanabahang-banner.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d940f3238be3_63cc52e0440ed70117e55523_carousel4.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95fa9238be0_63cc52e0d805d5e780eb6429_carousel5_0.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d94a35238be1_63cc52e00760e7cc4234f478_carousel1.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95c84238be4_63cc52e0d7632e1626418c7f_carousel3.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.w