      VALUES ('Thief Hotel', 'thief-hotel', '<p id="">A little islet, a sea of experiences. Boasting Oslo''s best location at Tjuvholmen near the Astrup Fearnley Museum, THE THIEF steals its guests away from the daily grind! Enjoy great facilities including 114 rooms and suites. We are a cash-free hotel.</p>', '<p><strong>The Thief Hotel</strong>&nbsp;offers quality accommodations and great service. The hotel is located 0,5 km from the city center and provides accessibility to important town facilities. No less exceptional is the hotel''s easy access to the city''s myriad of attractions and landmarks, such as Tjuvholmen Neighbourhood, Gerhardsen Gerner Oslo and Gallery Semmingsen.<br /><br />Simply put,&nbsp;all the services and amenities you have come to expect from Design Hotels are&nbsp;available at the Thief Hotel. To name a few of the hotel''s facilities, there is 24-hour room service, free Wi-Fi in all rooms, 24-hour security, car power charging stations and a convenience store.<br /><br />Guests can choose from 116 rooms, all of which exude an atmosphere of total peace and harmony. Whether you''re a fitness enthusiast or are just looking for a way to unwind after a hard day, you will be entertained by top-class recreational facilities such as boats, hot tub, fitness center, sauna and a golf course (within 3 km).&nbsp;<strong>The Thief Hotel</strong>&nbsp;is your one-stop destination for quality hotel accommodations in Oslo.</p>', 'https://media-dev.exploro.com/inflight-media/Oslo_The+Thief+Hotel+.mp4_0.mp4', '', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d940f3238be3_63cc52e0440ed70117e55523_carousel4.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95fa9238be0_63cc52e0d805d5e780eb6429_carousel5_0.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d94a35238be1_63cc52e00760e7cc4234f478_carousel1.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95c84238be4_6