      VALUES ('Thon Hotel Bristol', 'thon-hotel-bristol', '<p id="">The venerable Hotel Bristol is located in the heart of Oslo. The hotel has recently been modernised and upgraded, while the hotel’s traditional identity has been suitably preserved. Sample seasonally-based dishes in the restaurant, or enjoy refreshments to the sound of live piano music in the Library Bar.</p>', '<p>The venerable Hotel Bristol opened its doors for the first time in 1920. With much history permeating the walls, an upgraded interior and an elegant atmosphere, we will take you back in time. The hotel has large, comfortable rooms and suites, a fully-equipped fitness room, in addition to well-appointed conference and function rooms. Visit the Bristol Grill where you can sample seasonally-based dishes and delicious cakes. Vinterhaven and Biblioteksbaren serve refreshments to live piano music. All rooms newly renovated year 2019.</p>', 'https://media-dev.exploro.com/inflight-media/Oslo_Thon+Hotel+Bristol_.mp4.mp4', '', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d940f3238be3_63cc52e0440ed70117e55523_carousel4.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95fa9238be0_63cc52e0d805d5e780eb6429_carousel5_0.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d94a35238be1_63cc52e00760e7cc4234f478_carousel1.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95c84238be4_63cc52e0d7632e1626418c7f_carousel3.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d970ed238be2_63cc52e00760e7280834f479_carousel2.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cb05648e226c0f78efe3f1_hotel_4.jpeg', ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5ac08de9f2d81a3c8e96_63cb7b08d7632edf2133f782_6.png; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5ac08de9f2b7723c8e95_63cb7b055c439a4aac82bb90_7.png; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be35