      VALUES ('Trademark Hotel', 'trademark-hotel', '<p id="">A member of design hotels and Marriott Bonvoy, the 215-room urban business hotel is inspired by the cultural and creative renaissance in Nairobi, reflecting the City''s industrious and innovative nature through it''s design.</p>', '<p>Located in the lush suburbs of Nairobi, Trademark, an intellectual property by Tribe, is a 215-urban business hotel that boasts cultural and creative renaissance. The hotel offers 2 restaurants; each rated under Nairobi’s top 10. Harvest is inspired by the Kenyan''s true love for meat. It is a tribute to local farmers, the open grill Brasserie focuses on the farm fresh ingredients paired together to take you on a true culinary journey.</p><p>Hero, a new kind of eatery; the intersection of design, fantasy, indulgence &amp; individuality. The menu adopts the sushi form, but takes it out of its native context to give way to more flavor, color &amp; fun. Hero is located on the 9th floor, by the rooftop pool. Trademark hotel offers inspiring spaces, with 9 meeting rooms &amp; the iconic Trademark ballroom which can fit up to 500 people. The Trademark Club house is the focal point of our VIP service, located independently on the 10th floor overlooking Nairobi''s breathtaking skyline. All rooms are designed with the business traveler in mind, furnished with comfortable king-size beds, workstations, complimentary Wi-Fi.</p><p>You can contact us or visit our website for further information.</p>', 'https://media-dev.exploro.com/inflight-media/HERO-Web-66.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cb055f3f5ddf75416cc46d_HERO-Web-66.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d940f3238be3_63cc52e0440ed70117e55523_carousel4.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d95fa9238be0_63cc52e0d805d5e780eb6429_carousel5_0.jpeg; https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63cc5abf0949d94a35238be